Package: gander
Title: LLMs at the tooltip
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Simon", "Couch", , "simon.couch@posit.co", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5676-5107"))
Description: The package brings elmer chats into your RStudio and Positron
    sessions, editing files directly. After triggering the package addin, type
    your request and the assistant will stream its response directly into your
    documents, optionally incorporating context from the active file and
    its neighboring files.
